{"_id":"1OdEFpyyVOhLwx1T","name":"Scout","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Someone needs to find the way, to mark the route and lead others on. That's what you do. Every army needs you, the pathfinder, the scout. The spoor of many a beast is known to you, worse luck.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A rugged pony, camping gear and a small tent, dice for those quiet nights.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"7nrWBOzt4bIIXOvv","name":"Outlaw Chief","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>Amongst criminals and killers, you're the boss. They listen to you, or at least they do as long as you find easy pickings for them. They'll be quick to turn on you if things don't go well. So make sure the money flows...</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A sturdy, well-made bow, a gaggle of followers and a hideout somewhere in the forest.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BRV8NvsVpwZEbgHY","name":"Highwayman","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>A king of the road, you hold up coaches and rob their ride clients. Some see you as a romantic, and swoon at the sight of you. Others as a thief, vagabond and cut-throat, nothing more, nothing less. You don't care, as long as they have something worth taking.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A finely crafted sword, a face mask, a tricorn hat and a fast horse.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JWsIF44JVHaNoF7j","name":"Freelance","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are an armoured knight who pledges allegiance to whomever please you. As long as they pay enough to maintain your armour and your steed, you can afford to be picky. Maybe you fight for those of noble heart, maybe not. The choice is yours.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A finely crafted sword, plate armour and shield (heavy armour), and a warhorse. A colourful tent and camping gear.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JYPA7ZV1f0BJdbiR","name":"Veteran Soldier","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>War breeds warriors, and corpses. Luckily for you, you are the former, not the latter. The wars of the Kingdom have left you with many a scar and a tale to tell. Not that you tell them. Some stories are best kept to yourself.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Heavily used arming sword, mail and plate armour (heavy armour), Camping gear and a good pipe of tobacco.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LJ7xdbzNmvyEmprx","name":"Merchant","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've gone up in the world. No more hawking rubbish for you, you are a person of quality, a true trader, and people know it. You don't sell the things you trade, you talk about them. Others deal in the grubby business of selling.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Burgher's clothes, a writ of trade, a wagon and a warehouse.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MFBngI2gsIKYLFva","name":"Spy","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>In the back-streets of the capital, in the passages of the palace, or on some foreign shore. You know where to go and who to speak with to find out what you need. And if you need something for your masters, easily done.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: Nondescript clothing, heavy cloak, poisoned dagger, and a concealed tube for vital messages.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Survival":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Swimming":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Thrown":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0}}},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"HcHB4gb18gtp2Q2n":3},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"PyCzhywq4KduBhNQ","name":"Mercenary Captain","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You're the Captain because you outlived the rest. Or maybe because you shout the loudest. Either way, people look up to you now. Not nice people, but people all the same.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A rough and ready sword, a battered suit of plate (heavy armour) and a baton of command.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLeve