{"_id":"PyN2VwmFD2vtLb5L","name":"Charlatan","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are good at getting people to believe what you tell them, usually so that you can get them to buy what you sell them. Some consider you a criminal, but you don't - you're much more refined than that.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A suit of fine quality clothes, a tall fashionable hat, a discreet arming sword.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":t