{"_id":"dQ2cWSJPvlTSo91F","name":"Wizard","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You've collected enough spells, and learnt enough of the otherworld, to call yourself a wizard. Now others tremble at your power. As long as you don't make a mistake casting your spells, the world is at your feet. Just don't make a mistake...</p>\n<p>Required equipment: At least five spells, numerous scraps of mystical writings and fake spells, a staff inset with a jewel to show others of your power.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLeve