{"_id":"jZ2yowL0CWo7bHNK","name":"Bravo","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are a street fighter, flashy and grinning. You consider yourself a cut above the rest, but others see you just as a thug or assassin. More fool them. You're a king of the streets, strutting and brave, and you should be treated as such.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A fine arming sword, flashy clothes and a jaunty hat.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSki