{"_id":"jZcgCfcIARXwlwZC","name":"Assassin","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You are a killer, nothing more, nothing less. A killer for money. What else is there to kill for? The Kingdom has plenty of people that others want dead, for a myriad of reasons. You simply make sure that it happens, for gold.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A poison kit and blade, a mask, a disguise kit.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximu