{"_id":"uPTmGseFzew2aJNe","name":"Watch Captain","type":"Career","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","data":{"description":"<p>You command the watch, or at least can do so if you so choose. You are a hardened veteran, tough and uncompromising, and you are used to commanding others. They better listen, or else.</p>\n<p>Required equipment: A suit of fine quality mail and plate (modest armour), a commander's baton, a fine arming sword.</p>","isActive":false,"currentLevel":0,"activeSystem":"warlock","adventuringSkills":{"Appraise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Athletics":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bargain":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Blunt":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Bow":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Brawling":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Command":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Crossbow":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Diplomacy":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Disguise":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Dodge":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Endurance":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"History":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Incantation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Intimidate":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Language":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Large blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Lie":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Medicine":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Navigation":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Ostler":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":14},"Persuasion":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Pole arm":{"isCareerSkill":true,"maximumLevel":16},"Repair":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Sleight of hand":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Small blade":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Spot":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Stealth":{"isCareerSkill":false,"maximumLevel":0},"Streetwise":{"isCareerSkill":